<chapter xml:id="_basic_formatting">
<title>Basic Formatting</title>
<simpara>Writing a basic text with Asciidoctor is similar to what you&#8217;d do in Slack. You
can emphasize <emphasis>important messages with italic</emphasis>, <emphasis role="strong">even more important ones
with bold</emphasis>, <emphasis role="strong"><emphasis>combining them is not recommended</emphasis></emphasis> though. <literal>Monospace is the
right choice if you want to sound like a machine.</literal></simpara>
<simpara>Linebreaks
(enters)
are
ignored in output. So are      too    many   spaces. If you want to start a new
paragraph, leave an empty line.</simpara>
