<chapter xml:id="_breaking_the_natural_flow">
<title>Breaking the natural flow</title>
<section xml:id="_admonitions">
<title>Admonitions</title>
<note>
<simpara>Admonitions are these nice blocks of content prepended by icon telling you
to beware.</simpara>
</note>
<important>
<simpara>Using admonitions may help people realize there&#8217;s something of
importance going on.</simpara>
</important>
<tip>
<simpara>You can even include complex multiparagraph content in your admonitions.</simpara>
<simpara>Things such as:</simpara>
<itemizedlist>
<listitem>
<simpara>lists</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>images</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>tables</simpara>
</listitem>
<listitem>
<simpara>or even other admonitions</simpara>
</listitem>
</itemizedlist>
<caution>
<simpara>It might be confusing for your readers if you overdo it.</simpara>
</caution>
</tip>
<warning>
<simpara>Don&#8217;t overuse them.</simpara>
</warning>
</section>
